			//Wait 部分
			.wait
				.container
					h3.text-center.
						Wait!
						<br/>
						You don't need to answer every email as soon as it hits your inbox.
					.row
						.col-md-5
							img(src="../src/img/iphone-on-table-small.png")
						.col-md-7
							p.
								That's why we've reimagined your inbox and created Agenda View to let you know at a glance which emails are important and when you need to deal with them. With Timyo, you can communicate more meaningfully by sending and receiving emails with clear expectations that are already prioritized by time.
								<br/>
								<br/>
								Now you can focus on the email that matters, when it matters.
			// Focuson 部分
			.focus.container
				.container
					.h4#h4.text-center Focus on What matters today
					<br/>
					.text-center
						a.see(href="###") See how Timyo helps you
							span.glyphicon.glyphicon-play-circle
				<br/>
				.container.row
					.col-md-5.text-center
						img(src="../src/img/focus-on-what-matters.jpg")
					ul.col-md-7.list-unstyled.features-right
						li
							a.blue(href="#")
								img(src="../src/img/blue-box.png")
								span Manage important email by time
								span.glyphicon.glyphicon-play-circle
							p.blue-part.
								No need to clean out your inbox. Select only the emails that matter to you, assign a date and don't worry about the rest.
						li
							a.yellow(href="#")
								img(src="../src/img/yellow-box.png")
								span Receive email already prioritized by time
								span.glyphicon.glyphicon-play-circle
							p.blue-part.
								Timyo users send and receive emails that are already prioritized by time.
								Send email with clear expectations and receive better replies.
						li
							a.green(href="#")
								img(src="../src/img/green-box.png")
								span Oversee email through Agenda View
								span.glyphicon.glyphicon-play-circle
							p.blue-part.
								Stay organized at a glance!Use Agenda View to easily manage your time without leaving your inbox.
						li
							a.red(href="#")
								img(src="../src/img/red-box.png")
								span Get reminders on pending replies
								span.glyphicon.glyphicon-play-circle
							p.blue-part.
								Because your email is sent with clear expectations, Reply Tracker lets you know when a reply is still pending or overdue. 
			// 一台Mac部分
