									img(src="../src/img/red-box.png")
									span Existing account
								p Timyo isn't another new email address to manage — it's a way to better manage your existing accounts.
							li
								.firstpart
									img(src="../src/img/red-box.png")
									span Free & Flexible
								p You can switch back and forth between Timyo and your providers' apps whenever you want to (but we don't think you'll want to).
							li
